<form>	

	<input						FormControl (each input type is equal to FormControl)
	<textarea
	<select
	<button
	
</form>



FormGroup =>

a collection of form controls
(a form tag or group of form tags is addressed with the help of FormGroup, can nested in case of Complex objects)




FormControl =>

a class (its constructor take two params, 1st one is default value and 2nd one is validations)
(each input type is equal to FormControl)
